sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant ServiceA
    participant ServiceB
    participant LogAggregator

    User->>ServiceA: Emit structured log
    ServiceA->>LogAggregator: Send log data
    LogAggregator-->>ServiceA: Acknowledge receipt

    User->>ServiceB: Emit structured log
    ServiceB->>LogAggregator: Send log data
    LogAggregator-->>ServiceB: Acknowledge receipt